{"tid":1944541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有個手足戴晒架生用單手彈願榮光 !","createTime":"2020-03-26T12:46:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T19:01:00.000Z","uid":33484,"like":30,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e53d5927ab95a5f5c2e6e53cdb041e0d81df876a","tid":1944541,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:46:20.000Z","msg":"個手足就係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人<br />\n自去年六月開始同暴政抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n轉眼已踏入第九個月<br />\n一直以來<br />\n我哋打著「兄弟爬山，各自努力」嘅旗號<br />\n先可以走到今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n令暴政打散抗爭嘅陰謀始終未能得逞<br />\n或許時間耐咗<br />\n大家因意見相左而有所爭吵<br />\n而對家亦乘虛而入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時刻圖謀分化大家<br />\n所以今日送上願榮光嘅單手版<br />\n前後段因應音域而分別用左右手彈奏<br />\n寓意「兄弟爬山，各自努力」<br />\n寄望大家繼續齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n喺黑暗中迎接黎明來到之時<br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0DlcE9K_ZkM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0DlcE9K_ZkM&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=4217099f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0DlcE9K_ZkM</a>"},{"pid":"ea0435cf4373e14f5664854579be492ffd3e23e3","tid":1944541,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T12:53:51.000Z","msg":"輕輕一推"},{"pid":"c531b21644e430d6de242f10c9ff384f748489e2","tid":1944541,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:00:23.000Z","msg":"輕輕再推"},{"pid":"fdd3f8fbc5378bcb49e51ac4b468974a0a51db45","tid":1944541,"uid":33484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T13:13:11.000Z","msg":"一推再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c78827a1ae0d63ff974e28d6d45bebbf2ed18861"